{"tid":2329565,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"銀赫告白：和你在一起的每天都很美好","createTime":"2020-12-17T09:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T18:48:21.000Z","uid":74065,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c0426eed89078ed46c6674e5d058210425e1f344","tid":2329565,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:58:42.000Z","msg":"韓團Super Junior今年迎來出道15週年紀念，由成員銀赫和東海組成的Super Junior D &amp; E也是受到大家喜愛的子團，16日直播中他們就談到從2011年共組子團至今的感想，結果一搭一唱引用起《孤單又燦爛的神－鬼怪》（簡稱《鬼怪》）經典告白句子，講完自己都笑成一片，但粉絲都很喜歡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5338/d5338821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5338%2Fd5338821.jpg&h=d9b517a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲銀赫和東海是粉絲很喜歡的組合。（圖／翻攝自銀赫IG）<br />\n<br />\n銀赫、東海16日在Instagram開聯合直播，結果就這樣聊起來，東海開口就問「這9年來怎麼樣呀？」見銀赫思考一下只簡單回答「很好」進而追問哪些部分，機智的銀赫馬上就壓低嗓音引用《鬼怪》中的名句：「因為天氣很好，因為天氣不好，因為天氣剛剛好，和你在一起的每天都很美好。」<br />\n<br />\n一說完銀赫就唱起《鬼怪》OST《Beautiful》，東海也跟著合音，演完這齣後銀赫才驚覺在直播：「等等！你這樣跟我講話不就只是我們在視訊通話！」可是說完這句他們還是自顧自的聊起天來，不過很習慣這樣互動的粉絲看了也覺得很開心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5338/d5338822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5338%2Fd5338822.jpg&h=573a1047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲銀赫在直播用《鬼怪》句子告白東海。（圖／翻攝自elf__hasu推特）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，Super Junior D &amp; E出道於2011年，出道曲《Oppa, Oppa》充滿中毒性的旋律和歌詞掀起一陣模仿風潮，後續他們也陸續嘗試不同的風格，幾乎每年就會推出新作品，更成功在日本舉行3次巡迴演唱會、1次亞洲巡迴演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n▼銀赫、東海在Instagram引用《鬼怪》經典台詞。（影片／取自elf__hasu推特，如遭刪除請見諒）<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/elf__hasu/status/1339185240997154816?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1339185240997154816%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1878067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felf__hasu%2Fstatus%2F1339185240997154816%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1339185240997154816%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstar.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F1878067&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28Rn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=d84128df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felf__hasu%2Fstatus%2F1339185240997154816%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1339185240997154816%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstar.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F1878067&h=b4bf0649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/elf__hasu/status/1339185240997154816?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1339185240997154816%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1878067</a>"},{"pid":"439b0a98fbd682b573a01b9a2b1bc48e2d467596","tid":2329565,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:03:42.000Z","msg":"嘔心到"},{"pid":"2e0b7379831cc6be6986c2a48b0da7d1df2ae48e","tid":2329565,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"439b0a98fbd682b573a01b9a2b1bc48e2d467596","tid":2329565,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:03:42.000Z","msg":"嘔心到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:37:52.000Z","msg":"佢好煩"},{"pid":"27dfa683c31083f8a7176cd87a8852529c074b6b","tid":2329565,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"439b0a98fbd682b573a01b9a2b1bc48e2d467596","tid":2329565,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:03:42.000Z","msg":"嘔心到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:28:06.000Z","msg":"唔好逼我打9你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f68942f3e5c352e203b79f1c821c6f3dbf71f6c","tid":2329565,"uid":138302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:26:23.000Z","msg":"好襯"},{"pid":"d0093ba0dff4a4effcc34e1e30